                "invention-title": [
                    "Self-bias photoelectrocatalysis system based on (In) GaN nano-pillar array and application of self-bias photoelectrocatalysis system",
                    "一种基于（In）GaN纳米柱阵列的自偏压光电催化体系及其应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a self-bias photoelectrocatalysis system based on an (In) GaN nanorod array and application thereof. The self-bias photoelectrocatalysis system comprises the following components: a photoanode and a photocathode, the photo-anode comprises at least one of integration of a single electrode of the (In) GaN nano-pillar array and the Si-based solar cell, integration of double electrodes of the (In) GaN nano-pillar array and the Si-based solar cell, and integration of the single electrode of the (In) GaN nano-pillar array and the double electrodes of the (In) GaN nano-pillar array; the photocathode comprises at least one of an (In) GaN nanorod photocathode and a platinum electrode. And the self-bias photoelectrocatalytic hydrogen production is realized by simulating sunlight to irradiate the photoelectrode. According to the invention, a self-bias photoelectrocatalysis system based on the (In) GaN nanorod array is used, the spectrum absorption can be broadened, the photovoltage required by water decomposition can be improved, the hydrogen production by self-bias photoelectricity water decomposition can be realized, and an effective strategy is provided for large-scale preparation of hydrogen energy by using solar energy."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种基于(In)GaN纳米柱阵列的自偏压光电催化体系及其应用，包括以下组件：光阳极和光阴极；光阳极包括(In)GaN纳米柱阵列的单电极与Si基太阳能电池的集成、(In)GaN纳米柱阵列的双电极与Si基太阳能电池的集成、(In)GaN纳米柱阵列的单电极和(In)GaN纳米柱阵列的双电极中的至少一种；光阴极包括(In)GaN纳米柱光阴极和铂电极中的至少一种。通过模拟太阳光照射光电极实现自偏压光电催化产氢。本发明使用基于(In)GaN纳米柱阵列的自偏压光电催化体系，能拓宽光谱吸收、提高水分解所需光电压，实现自偏压光电水分解产氢，为利用太阳能大规模制备氢能源提供有效策略。"
                }
            ]
